text: Thibaut Amani Danho (born 15 January 1994) is an Ivorian competitive swimmer. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 100 metre freestyle. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Ivorian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Ivory Coast Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Male freestyle swimmers
